00%;padding-bottom:52.34375%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/85b06/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 256w,\n/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/bc282/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 512w,\n/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/f1720/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 1024w,\n/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/5ece7/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/85b06/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 256w,\n/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/bc282/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 512w,\n/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/f1720/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 1024w,\n/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/5ece7/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 1200w\" src=\"/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/f1720/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png\" alt=\"An image of Tim Duncan, Manu Ginobili, and Tony Parker at the 2021 Basketball Hall of Fame Enshrinement Ceremony with a black and gold border and gold lettering\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/85b06/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 256w,\n/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/bc282/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 512w,\n/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/f1720/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 1024w,\n/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/5ece7/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/85b06/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 256w,\n/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/bc282/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 512w,\n/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/f1720/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 1024w,\n/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/5ece7/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png 1200w\" src=\"/static/2e380e1970cc1aefba4b68e2931d8f93/f1720/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony.png\" alt=\"An image of Tim Duncan, Manu Ginobili, and Tony Parker at the 2021 Basketball Hall of Fame Enshrinement Ceremony with a black and gold border and gold lettering\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tim_Duncan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tim Duncan</a></strong> was just enshrined into the <strong><a href=\"https://www.nba.com/news/paul-pierce-chris-bosh-and-chris-webber-headline-2021-hof-class\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Basketball Hall of Fame</a></strong> with two more prominent San Antonio Spurs players waiting in the wings!  Tim was accompanied by the Admiral himself, <strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Robinson\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">David Robinson</a>, </strong>who entered the Basketball Hall of Fame in 2009. Tim and David won two NBA championships together in 1999 and 2003.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The infamous ‘Iceman’ <strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Gervin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">George Gervin</a></strong> is the only other San Antonio Spurs player currently enshrined in the Hall of Fame, at this time, but as we expect that won’t be for long!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tony_Parker\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tony Parker</a></strong> and <strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manu_Gin%C3%B3bili\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Manu Ginobili</a></strong> are a lock to be first ballot Hall of Fame selections in the next couple of years. That will unite the “Big Three” of Duncan, Parker and Ginobili in Springfield, Massachusetts for all-time!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The PM Group was very fortunate to be the <a href=\"https://www.nba.com/spurs/\"><strong>San Antonio Spurs </strong></a>advertising agency of record for 7 years during the greatest era of their success on the court. It was an honor to be a part of an organization that has done so much for the San Antonio community and brought invaluable attention to our city across the country and the world. Basketball has truly united us all we’ll keep rooting on our Spurs through the seasons.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">About The PM Group</a>:</strong> The PM Group was founded in 1988. For over 33 years, the agency has continued to grow and is San Antonio’s largest marketing and advertising agency. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including home services, automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profits, real estate and fitness. For two consecutive years now, the Agency has set annual revenue records with the addition of six new clients and through the continued success of our existing clients. Additionally, the agency hosts their annual Charity Gala that to date has raised millions of dollars for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! In 2020 alone, the Agency donated over $1,050,000 to local non-profits. It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"One Down, Two to Go!","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"One Down, Two to Go!","url":"/one-down-two-to-go/"}],"title":"Tim Duncan Enshrined into Basketball Hall of Fame | The PM Group","metaDesc":"Tim Duncan was recently enshrined into the Basketball Hall of Fame. The San Antonio Spurs were a client of The PM Group during the team’s greatest era.","focuskw":"Basketball Hall of Fame","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"Tim Duncan Enshrined into Basketball Hall of Fame | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"Tim Duncan was recently enshrined into the Basketball Hall of Fame. The San Antonio Spurs were a client of The PM Group during the team’s greatest era.","opengraphImage":{"altText":"An image of Tim Duncan at the 2020 Basketball Hall of Fame Enshrinement Ceremony on a gold background","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony-Square.jpg","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony-Square-300x300.jpg 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony-Square-150x150.jpg 150w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Image-5.19.21-Basketball-Hall-of-Fame-Ceremony-Square.jpg 708w"},"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":null,"canonical":"/one-down-two-to-go/","cornerstone":false,"schema":{"raw":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"/#website\",\"url\":\"/\",\"name\":\"The PM Group\",\"description\":\"San Antonio\\u2019s Largest Advertising and Marketing Agency\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"SearchAction\",\"target\":{\"@type\":\"EntryPoint\",\